<%- include('header', {
  pageClass: 'app-shell about-shell',
  mobileMenuTitle: 'About app',
  mobileMenuLinks: [
    { label: 'Open dashboard', href: '/To-do' },
    { label: 'Logout', href: '/logout' }
  ]
}); -%>
<main class="about-page">
  <section class="about-card">
    <p class="eyebrow">Behind the build</p>
    <h1>Made with care by Hemant.</h1>
    <p class="about-copy">
      This to-do app is built to feel fast, focused, and a little dramatic in the best way. Clean lists, better pacing,
      command-deck shortcuts, privacy veil mode, spotlight task picking, and tighter session hardening now make the
      board feel more like a personal control room than a basic checklist.
    </p>
    <div class="about-actions">
      <a class="ghost-link" href="/To-do">
        <svg class="lucide-icon lucide-icon--button" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
          <rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7" rx="1.5" />
          <rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7" rx="1.5" />
          <rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7" rx="1.5" />
          <rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7" rx="1.5" />
        </svg>
        <span>Open dashboard</span>
      </a>
      <a class="ghost-link" href="/logout">
        <svg class="lucide-icon lucide-icon--button" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="m16 17 5-5-5-5" />
          <path d="M21 12H9" />
          <path d="M13 5V4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H5a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h6a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-1" />
        </svg>
        <span>Logout</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
<%- include('footer'); -%>
